61\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-acdd388\" data-id=\"acdd388\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae4db0d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ae4db0d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Shamrock'N Bar Crawl \u2013 The only day we're all a wee bit o'Irish!<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-ba5f203 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ba5f203\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-4cff59b\" data-id=\"4cff59b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3a67a75 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3a67a75\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ShamrockN-Bar-Crawl-.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16807\" alt=\"Shamrock&#039;N Bar Crawl Beaver Dam, Wisconsin\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ShamrockN-Bar-Crawl-.png 500w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/ShamrockN-Bar-Crawl--150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-cd010e5\" data-id=\"cd010e5\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1fbfe28 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1fbfe28\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Saturday, March 14 | 3:00 PM \u2013 10:00 PM |<\/strong><strong>\u00a0Ages 21+<br \/>Shuttle starts at 4:00 PM &#8211; later shuttle will be available with less frequent stops<\/strong><\/p><p>Get ready for Beaver Dam\u2019s biggest St. Patrick\u2019s celebration. The Shamrock\u2019N Bar Crawl returns with festive drink specials, live music, themed parties, delicious food, and a full evening of green\u2011filled fun across your favorite local bars and restaurants. <em><strong>The event officially begins at 3:00 PM, with free trolley and shuttle service starting at 4:00 PM.<\/strong><\/em><\/p><p>Whether you&#8217;re a local or visiting for the holiday, this is your chance to explore Beaver Dam\u2019s nightlife, enjoy exclusive specials, and celebrate St. Paddy\u2019s Day in style.<\/p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Participating Locations &amp; Specials<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p>TBD<\/p><p><strong>Make a Scene in Green Costume Contest!<\/strong> Show off your best St. Patrick\u2019s Day attire. Take a photo at Dragon\u2019s Den Lounge between 5 PM and 6:30 PM. Contest winner chosen by Facebook voting. Winner announced Tuesday after the event,<\/p><p><strong>Join the Fun!<\/strong> Gather your friends, put on your most festive green gear, and celebrate across Beaver Dam\u2019s best bars and venues. This is the perfect way to kick off St. Patrick\u2019s week with drinks, entertainment, and community spirit.<\/p><p><strong>Disclaimer:<\/strong>\u00a0 Drink and food specials are subject to change at the discretion of each venue.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-6b21c55 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"6b21c55\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-243697b\" data-id=\"243697b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c026ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6c026ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Monster Bar Crawl - A \"Spine Tingling Night of Fun!\"<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-17ff11c elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"17ff11c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8dc0942\" data-id=\"8dc0942\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-b696085 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b696085\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-8c0a616\" data-id=\"8c0a616\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-559d0ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"559d0ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Monster-Bar-Crawl-2024-4.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-15985\" alt=\"Monster Bar Crawl, Fall Downtown Fest, Beaver Dam Wisconsin\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Monster-Bar-Crawl-2024-4.png 900w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Monster-Bar-Crawl-2024-4-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-43dce33\" data-id=\"43dce33\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-756116c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"756116c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\">\ud83c\udf83 <b>Beaver Dam Monster Bar Crawl | <\/b><b>Friday, October 30, 2026 | 5 PM \u2013 11 PM <\/b>\ud83d\udc7b No ticket required \u2013 just show up in costume and join the crawl!<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\ud83d\ude8c <b>TROLLEY &amp; SHUTTLE STOPS<\/b><br \/>Ride safely between locations with our courtesy shuttle.<br \/>Please tip your driver! (Thanks to <b>Johnny\u2019s Lounge &amp; PS Events<\/b> for transportation.)<br \/>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <b>S. Spring St.<\/b> @ Palenque \u2013 includes Ooga Brewing Company &amp; Dragon\u2019s Den Lounge<br \/>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <b>Front St.<\/b> by Stormy\u2019s Parking Lot<br \/>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <b>Burnett Street<\/b> \u2013 Charlie Brown\u2019s<br \/>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <b>Mill Street<\/b> \u2013 Blue Hawaii<br \/>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<b> Thirsty Beaver Stop<\/b> \u2013 includes Johnny\u2019s Lounge &amp; Dam Tavern<\/p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">\ud83c\udf7b<\/span> <b>DRINK SPECIALS &amp; ACTIVITIES <\/b><b>COMING SOON! <\/b><\/p><p><span class=\"s1\">\ud83d\udeab<\/span> <b>SAFETY REMINDERS<\/b><br \/>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <b>Must be 21+ with valid ID at each bar<\/b><br \/><b>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 No drinks may be taken beyond bar premises<\/b><br \/><b>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Don\u2019t drink and drive \u2013 arrange safe transportation: Call Julie for Safe Ride at 920-210-3189<\/b><b><\/b><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Ultimate Beaver Dam Crawl Guide Drink local, crawl responsibly Must be 21 years of age to participate in our bar crawls. Beaver Bar Crawl \u2013 &#8220;Busy Beavers on the Loose&#8221; \ud83d\udcc5 Date: April 25 |\u00a0 12:00 PM \u2013 5:00 PM\ud83d\udccd Location: Participating bars &amp; restaurants in Beaver Dam (full list coming soon!) \ud83d\udce2 Important [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":34,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-14860","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"meta_box":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14860","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/34"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14860"}],"version-history":[{"count":151,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14860\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":16980,"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14860\/revisions\/16980"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14860"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}